snippet.title: Star Man 2: Reupgraded - Mercury Trailer
snippet.description: After many months, I've made some more progress on my fangame project. Introducing Star Man 2's freshest update, complete with a new graphical style! Visit our Discord server at https://discord.gg/hEtemS3 for more frequent updates.
